{"tid":2313482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"牛頭角銀包離奇失蹤4 12","createTime":"2020-12-05T20:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T20:25:46.000Z","uid":378485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe664166bc32e040ad774883fc5efc41b96e1418","tid":2313482,"uid":378485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:23:05.000Z","msg":"今日塔38往平田方向 巴士嗰時 突然諗住帶我嗰fd行下觀濱（話哂觀濱都係一嗰一去難忘嘅地方）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就嗱嗱臨係牛頭角落車帶佢去觀濱攞佢第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落車嗰時懶醒咁望望有冇留野(冇），屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行觀濱行到半路摸摸自己先至銀包唔撚見咗<br />\n咁咪即刻返原路同call埋總站 (可能係鄧底）上車睇埋 都冇 問下嗰站長仲好撚串咁同我講-冇就冇㗎la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都頹咗 認命去報失<br />\n去到狗屋見到有嗰手足去保釋報到 見到好撚心噏 <br />\n<br />\n平時都算係好彩嘅人，不過係唔見野方面未遇過好心人會聯絡我<br />\n心淡淡哋<br />\n攞錢都算證件都唔放嗰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S9mBcao.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS9mBcao.png&h=b37fe00c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇諗過會揾得返 隨緣"},{"pid":"35dc17b3ec6c5962ca700032b55b66464b82140c","tid":2313482,"uid":378485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8198fd342c91125a28e59b5f42320fcaeec76a63","tid":2313482,"uid":302151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:25:46.000Z","msg":"睇左做牛角包銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}